SSEEEE AALLSSOO
       The  full  documentation  for ddff is maintained as a Texinfo manual.  If the iinnffoo and ddff programs are properly installed at your site, the
       command

              iinnffoo ccoorreeuuttiillss ''ddff iinnvvooccaattiioonn''

       should give you access to the complete manual.



